      "rationale": "A three-level mesh refinement study (coarse: ~45k elements, medium: ~180k elements, fine: ~720k elements) was conducted. Force at 40 mm displacement changed by 1.4% between medium and fine meshes. Richardson extrapolation yielded a grid convergence index of 0.8%, well below the 2% threshold."
