      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties sourced from certified coupon tests on same material lot; geometric dimensions from CMM measurements of test articles.",
      "rationale": "Elastic modulus (114 GPa), yield strength (880 MPa), and tangent modulus (1.2 GPa) were derived from tensile coupon tests on the same Ti-6Al-4V material lot used for the test constructs. Screw and rod geometry entered from CMM measurements with ±0.01 mm tolerance. Cortical bone block geometry from ASTM F1717 nominal dimensions confirmed by caliper measurement."
