      "rationale": "Eleven constructs assembled from production-representative non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screws and 5.5 mm titanium rods. Six constructs tested at Laboratory A (FDA), five at Laboratory B (DePuy Synthes). All hardware from the same manufacturing lot. Sample size exceeds the N=10 pre-specified minimum."
