      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Multiple loading rates or environmental conditions evaluated to characterize condition sensitivity.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single crosshead speed (5 mm/min) per ASTM F1717. No variation in loading rate, temperature, or simulated fluid environment was evaluated. This factor falls below the required level 2; however, quasi-static loading rate insensitivity for Ti-6Al-4V is well-documented in literature and the deviation is accepted with documented justification by the assessment team."
    },
