      "rationale": "Screw geometry in FEA derived from CMM data of the same hardware lot. Material properties from same-lot coupon tests. Boundary conditions replicate ASTM F1717 fixture kinematics: inferior block fixed, superior block constrained to translate along loading axis only. Torque applied to set screw captured via pre-tensioned contact. Equivalency confirmed by overlay of simulated and experimental fixture compliance curves."
