      "rationale": "Three QoIs evaluated: construct stiffness (E/uval = 1.18, 5.2% diff), yield force (E/uval = 1.29, 6.8% diff), and force at 40 mm displacement (E/uval = 1.41, 6.3% diff). All three satisfy both acceptance criteria. Validation uncertainty uval computed per ASME V&V 20 including experimental uncertainty (2.3%) and simulation numerical uncertainty (1.1%)."
